descriptionHtml:
Altmers are great... +50 Magicka is almost like 5 more levels !!!

Even if I was happy with the weird look of the skyrim elves, I wanted a beautiful face for my female avatar => a not so much alien-from-Roswell one... It was a quite a challenge and it took me some time. Here is it. I hope you will be as satisfied as me. 

Enjoy !

I advise you to use the smoother female mod. The screenshots are taken while using this mod.
http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=140

PS: The savegame is of course  at the begining of the story, inside the Helgen Keep, when your hands are free.
author: Eoloe
